data.description: Nestled in the coveted Bolsa Landmark development, this exclusive 4 bed, 3 bath haven is a sanctuary of comfort, style and charm. Tucked away in a quiet cul de sac, this home offers a warm welcome with its custom double Dutch-door entry, setting the tone for the luxurious living that awaits. The living and dining room areas are graced by a captivating fireplace with custom stone/tile work and mantle, making it the heart of the home. Skylights and volume ceilings bring an airy, open feel to the space, filling it with natural light. Next discover the meticulously remodeled kitchen that is sure to impress. The stone countertops and subway tile backsplash create an elegant backdrop for the stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets with mood lighting, wine fridge, farm sink and professional hardware complement the functionality of this gourmet space. An inviting eat in breakfast bar allows you to savor your morning coffee. The family room flows seamlessly into the kitchen, creating an ideal layout for entertaining and a well appointed bar/storage/pantry area enhance the practicality of the space. French doors lead from the family room to the private backyard. The backyard is a true retreat, featuring a sparkling pool and spa, complete with a soothing waterfall and with child proof safety netting, all controlled with remote smart phone capability. A new built-in firepit surrounded by a comfortable conversation/seating area provides the perfect setting for evening gatherings.  Lush landscaping creates a sense of privacy and serenity, making the outdoor space an extension of the tranquil interior. Versatility is at the forefront with a bed and bath downstairs, making the perfect accommodations for guests, in laws or a home office. The master suite is a true retreat. It boasts two closets with organizers, a stylish barn door entrance sets the tone for experience within. A custom vanity, and oversized walk in shower with designer tile accents create a spa like ambiance. The 3 car garage offers over 330 sq ft of additional storage space, epoxy flooring and 240V EV ready garage hook up.  Additional features include, crown moldings, recessed lighting, plantation shutters, new paint inside and out, wainscoting accents, newer roof, newer A/C with built in O-zone air scrubber system, remote key pad and garage access, side storage shed with electric power for e-bike storage, wired for alarm system and two heated outdoor shower heads on the side on the house. No HOA!
